    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Is BUPA's mental health coverage really unlimited?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">
        Yes, on Health+ and Elite+ plans, mental health has full parity with physical health. There's no separate annual limit or session cap. Your overall coverage limit applies (which is often unlimited), not a mental health sub-limit. This is rare in international insurance and a genuine BUPA advantage.
